# Configuration

## Checklist

- [ ] Variable `VITE_API_URL` configurada en `.env`
- [ ] `getApiUrl()` helper creado
- [ ] Axios client configurado con `withCredentials: true`
- [ ] `AuthContext` y `AuthProvider` creados
- [ ] `ProtectedRoutes` component creado
- [ ] `UserInfo` component creado
- [ ] `ErrorBoundary` creado
- [ ] `AuthProvider` envuelve la app en `App.tsx`
